<p>In the meantime, join us building OpenSearch (if you havenâ€™t already)! Feel free to take a look around at what the community has been up to, check out the public <a href="https://github.com/orgs/opensearch-project/projects/1">roadmap</a>, and then head over to look at the open issues. Or you could jump right in and start opening issues or contributing. For more details see <a href="https://github.com/opensearch-project/OpenSearch/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md">here</a>.</p>
